    <abstract>
      <t>One possible deployment strategy for BGP origin validation based on
      the Resource Public Key Infrastructure (RPKI) is the construction of
      islands of trust. This document describes the author's experience
      deploying and mantaining a BGP origin validation island of trust in
      Equator. </t>
    </abstract>
